text: Unako yasa kurama uni(sulaimana) hamsihale ra bhanna thaleh ki he palanakarta! Mala'i sakti de'u juna krpa timi mamathi ra mera ama babumathi gareka chau, tyasaprati krtajnata jnapana garum ra yasta asala kama garum ki tyasabata timi prasanna bha'ihala ra mala'i aphno krpale aphno asala dasaharuma pravesa gara'ihala
